subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: Which famous fort was built by Maharaja Ambaji in the 17th century?
question_hi: 17वें सदीमें महाराजा अम्बाजी ने किस महत्वपूर्ण किस्मत की बनी थी?
explanation_en:
Amber Fort, built by Maharaja Mansingh in the 16th century, is a famous landmark in Jaipur, Rajasthan. It is known for its intricate architecture and has been a significant part of Rajasthani culture.
